00:22:17,000 --> 00:22:21,000
We're all so proud of you, Mama, so darned happy.

640
00:22:21,000 --> 00:22:24,000
But you still got to be careful.

641
00:22:24,000 --> 00:22:25,000
You mustn't worry so much about Edmund.

642
00:22:25,000 --> 00:22:26,000
He'll be all right.

643
00:22:26,000 --> 00:22:28,000
Of course he'll be all right and I don't know what you mean

644
00:22:28,000 --> 00:22:31,000
warning me to be careful.

645
00:22:31,000 --> 00:22:34,000
All right, Mama.

646
00:22:34,000 --> 00:22:35,000
I'm sorry I spoke.

647
00:22:35,000 --> 00:22:48,000


648
00:22:48,000 --> 00:23:13,000
[COUGHING]

